{
  "texts": [
    "Co-Occurrence & Dependency AnalysisComparison of the co-occurrence strength in English privacy policies before and after the enforcement dates or, if not enforced at the time of writing, effectiveness dates of the GDPR and CCPA/CPRA as described in Section 4.4.2 revealed intriguing insights.",
    "Similarly to Wagner's work [76], we identified an increased co-occurrence of collect_precise location data in the January & February 2023 privacy policies.",
    "We additionally observed an increased exclusivity in cooccurrence strength for, e. g., collect_voice data, use_algorithm-based technology, and personalize_child, which would require more indepth investigation.",
    "Due to space constraints we list the observed occurrences of common verbs in privacy policies in Appendix H. Topic Changes over TimeIn Section 4.4.3, we described how we applied BERTopic to identify topic changes in privacy policies over time.",
    "Table 7 presents the number of topics identified by BERTopic in each corpus."
  ]
}